dct_title_s: Detail map of the upper Mississippi River from the mouth of the Ohio River to Minneapolis, Minnesota, v.1
dct_description_sm: Survey of the Mississippi River; made under the direction of the Mississippi River Commission. Contains Charts 101-134. Each chart is at a scale of 1:20,000. Charts also show river depths and include an Authorities and Notes section. Some charts show land owners adjacent to the river.
